title: Blackstar  {Complete Series}  DVDrip
description:
Blackstar was  produced by Filmation in 1981.An astronaut from a future version of Earth who had been swept through a black hole and stranded on the planet Sagar, where magic and sword and sorcery still ruled the day.Trapped on the planet Sagar, Blackstar is rescued by the tiny Trobbit people.In turn he joins their fight for freedom against the cruel Overlord who rules by the might of the Powerstar. The Powerstar is split into the Powersword and the Starsword. And so with Starsword in hand, Blackstar together with his allies, sets out to save the planet Sagar.
